headline: Assessing Paychex (PAYX) Valuation After Earnings Beat And New US$1b Buyback In A Soft Employment Backdrop
summary: Dividend declaration and buyback plan set the stage for Paychex stock debate Paychex (PAYX) is back in focus after reporting earnings that exceeded expectations, unveiling a new US$1b share repurchase authorization and reaffirming its regular quarterly dividend, even as economic concerns pressured the stock.
